Database Schemas:
    - Create database schemas diagram.
    - Create database schema migrations.
        - Migrations:
            - restaurants
            - products
            - orders
            - customers
            - messages
            - order_statuses
    - Create model and relations.
        - Models:
            - Restaurant
            - Product
            - Order
            - Customers
            - Messages

API Routes:
    - Create Restaurant POST
    - Create Product POST
    - Create Order POST
    - Create Customers POST
    - List Sent Messages GET
    - List Other Status Message GET

API Controllers:
    - Create Restaurant Controller Resource.
    - Create Product Controller Resource.
    - Create Order Controller Resource.
        - POST:
            - Insert order to the orders table.
            - Insert message to the messages table.
            - Send message to customer.
            - Listen message and update status.
        - PUT:
            - Update an order as delivered.
                - Add a message in queue that for send to customer after 90 minutes.
    - Create Customer Controller Resource.
    - Create Messages List Controller Resource.
        - GET:
            - Get last 50 sent messages.
            - Get messages of any other status in last 24 hours.

Notifications:
    - Install Nexmo package.
    - Register Nexmo for test.
    - Create Notification class.


Tests:
    - Write Unit tests

